85/490052_mini.png?m=1589765551", "bio": "", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/he110comex", "tagline": "", "twitter": "", "created": 1589763210, "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/7c05/2485/490052_mini.png?m=1589765551", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/7c05/2485/490052_mini.png?m=1589765551", "location": "", "btc": "", "id": 490052}, "last_reply_by": "qinxi", "last_touched": 1630133363, "title": "实测：通过换绑微信手机号可以开启 CallKit", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/798484", "created": 1630123715, "content": "微信 iOS 最新版\r\n手机号为 Google Voice\r\n\r\n方法及步骤：\r\n1 、国区手机号换绑为 GV，目前微信设置里面没有开启系统通话的选项；\r\n2 、大概 10 来分钟左右，再打开微信弹窗提示账号退出；\r\n3 、再次登录会弹出一个英文版的协议需要同意；\r\n4 、登录成功后，在设置选项能够找到「语音通话用系统电话接听」的选项；\r\n5 、测试锁屏接听微信语音通话；\r\n\r\n成功！\r\n\r\n设置及接听我刚截图（没有找到横向完整拼图的工具，竖着这样看吧），如下：\r\n\r\nhttps://i.imgur.com/TiBbrs5.png", "content_rendered": "微信 iOS 最新版<br />手机号为 Google Voice<br /><br />方法及步骤：<br />1 、国区手机号换绑为 GV，目前微信设置里面没有开启系统通话的选项；<br />2 、大概 10 来分钟左右，再打开微信弹窗提示账号退出；<br />3 、再次登录会弹出一个英文版的协议需要同意；<br />4 、登录成功后，在设置选项能够找到「语音通话用系统电话接听」的选项；<br />5 、测试锁屏接听微信语音通话；<br /><br />成功！<br /><br />设置及接听我刚截图（没有找到横向完整拼图的工具，竖着这样看吧），如下：<br /><br /><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://i.imgur.com/TiBbrs5.png\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/TiBbrs5.png\" class=\"embedded_image\" rel=\"noreferrer\"></a>", "last_modified": 1630123715, "replies": 33, "id": 798484}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_large.png?m=1615111825", "name": "apple", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_normal.png?m=1615111825", "title": "Apple", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/apple", "topics": 15657, "footer": "", "header": "设计了 <a href=\"/go/watch\">Apple Watch</a>，<a href=\"/go/ipad\">iPad</a>，<a href=\"/go/iphone\">iPhone</a>，<a href=\"/go/imac\">iMac</a> 及 <a href=\"/go/mbp\">MacBook Pro</a> 等电子产品的美国公司。", "title_alternative": "Apple", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_mini.png?m=1615111825", "stars": 1902, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 184, "parent_node_name": "hardware"}, "member": {"username": "neptuno", "website": null, "github": null, "psn": null, "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/9897/58ca/196464_mini.png?m=1535078743", "bio": null, "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/neptuno", "tagline": null, "twitter": null, "created": 1476627749, "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/9897/58ca/196464_mini.png?m=1535078743", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/9897/58ca/196464_mini.png?m=1535078743", "location": null, "btc": null, "id": 196464}, "last_reply_by": "p1gd0g", "last_touched": 1630102609, "title": "关于 ios 游戏充值", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/798359", "created": 1630048594, "content": "只是单纯对 ios 充值抽成机制和规定不了解，为什么王者等游戏不弄一个公众号充值，直接在公众号扣钱，购买对应区的点券，这样苹果就不抽成了。\r\n\r\n据我了解，b 站开通舰长就可以公众号上面操作\r\n\r\n（只是单纯好奇哈，有没有大佬愿意解惑？）", "content_rendered": "<p>只是单纯对 ios 充值抽成机制和规定不了解，为什么王者等游戏不弄一个公众号充值，直接在公众号扣钱，购买对应区的点券，这样苹果就不抽成了。</p>\n<p>据我了解，b 站开通舰长就可以公众号上面操作</p>\n<p>（只是单纯好奇哈，有没有大佬愿意解惑？）</p>\n", "last_modified": 1630048594, "replies": 33, "id": 798359}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/55b3/7c5c/649_large.png?m=1620805836", "name": "wechat", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/55b3/7c5c/649_normal.png?m=1620805836", "title": "微信", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/wechat", "topics": 2722, "footer": "", "header": "关于微信及微信小程序的讨论节点", "title_alternative": "WeChat", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/55b3/7c5c/649_mini.png?m=1620805836", "stars": 450, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 649, "parent_node_name": "internet"}, "member": {"username": "imTerry", "website": "", "github": null, "psn": null, "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/8113ccd959d525427e42f5fd27563b4a?s=24&d=retro", "bio": "", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/imTerry", "tagline": "", "twitter": null, "created": 1607867604, "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/8113ccd959d525427e42f5fd27563b4a?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_mini": "https:/